
Privacy Policy



tinyTerm does not collect any user data, except when logs are reqeusted for bug reports, 

debug logs are used for trouble shooting purpose only, data is ever shared with external 

parties unless explicitly requested by the user.



tinyTerm is hosted on GitHub and Microsoft Store, the use of those sites are governed by 

privacy policy of those sites, author of tinyTerm does not track or store data of users 

except to fulfill the user requested actions, or to aid in fixing technical problems.

 
